"Bind noh to <C-n>
map <C-n> :noh<CR> 

"Disable arrow-keys
map <up> <nop>
map <down> <nop>
map <left> <nop>
map <right> <nop>
imap <right> <nop>
imap <left> <nop>
imap <up> <nop>
imap <down> <nop>

"Map Ctrl+key to move between windows
map <C-j> <C-W>j
map <C-k> <C-W>k
map <C-h> <C-W>h
map <C-l> <C-W>l

" Remap 0 to first non-blank character
map 0 ^

"Treat long lines as break lines
map j gj
map k gk

" Keep selection after index
vnoremap < <gv
vnoremap > >gv

"Color related configs
syntax enable                   " Enable syntax highlighting
